{"tid":206818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(影片)曼谷「洗太平地」趕絕街邊檔 仲想掃街胡慧沖話嚟呢度！","createTime":"2017-04-18T14:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T05:35:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7bfc637615dbe797c8bbe6847f03e0a3607eca","tid":206818,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170418/large/1492508685_677d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170418%2Flarge%2F1492508685_677d.jpg&h=2465984b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">胡慧沖指，部分原本在街邊經營的小販，轉到持牌的夜市中經營。圖為曼谷「火車夜市」。（胡慧沖提供圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170418/large/1492507249_2ef6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170418%2Flarge%2F1492507249_2ef6.jpg&h=efae36bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">胡慧沖（小圖示）稱拉差裡威（Ratchathewi）附近地鐵站及水門街附近目前仍有夜市。</span><br />\n港人外遊勝地曼谷以夜市及街頭小食聞名，不過人頭踴踴在街邊「掃街」場面隨時絕跡。據外電報道，曼谷市政府因接獲大量公眾投訴，指小販在街邊擺賣涉衞生及秩序問題，決定在市內全面「洗太平地」，禁止小販在曼谷市內所有主要道路「擺檔」。<br />\n有「泰國通」之稱的旅居泰國港人胡慧沖指，聽聞市政府近日已宣佈禁止小販在街頭擺檔禁令。他說，其實當地政府在較早前已決心整頓市容，陸續在市內多個主要旅遊區「洗太平地」，原本在暹羅廣場（Siam Square）、是隆（Silom）夜市及水門街一帶經營的小販早已被政府下令取締。新一輪「洗太平地」計劃，則主要影響其餘較少旅客到的區域，唐人街一帶相信會也會是受影響範圍，但參考早前當地政府政府的「洗太平地」進度，需時約8個月左右，估計唐人街一帶小販暫時未受影響。<br />\n胡慧沖又指，雖然曼谷市內將有新商場開幕，但港人到當地旅遊，「始終鍾意掃街、去夜市，接觸多啲草根文化」，認為對旅客而言，洗太平地的確會失色；但對當地人而言，小販的確有擋路及衞生等問題，亦有居民覺得小販滋擾。<br />\n胡慧沖又為喜愛到曼谷「掃街」及行夜市的港人提供貼士，在曼谷地鐵拉差裡威站（Ratchathewi）附近，目前尚有小販擺檔；至於水門街「The Palladium World Shopping Mall」附近亦設有小夜市。  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170418/56580044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170418%2F56580044&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4waMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=28d70681\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170418%2F56580044&h=24e953bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170418/56580044</a>"},{"pid":"9cbc98c0e26b783c9dcde038aedf3b33fe6ab2d5","tid":206818,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792e0f8f0584727f8935f84783f6f831c210d364","tid":206818,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e0ae162e6a32bd5cc16d643178acf25931da92","tid":206818,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22aba9996b1d98e1a959fea0991a83c578a607e4","tid":206818,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2768a890a4f6494d7082a80438a61c0ea429cddc","tid":206818,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe361814a821daeebe1290038434ed9f22207d3","tid":206818,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好搞到好似新加坡hawker centre咁<br />\n管理過度，冇晒特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9746156ef07dd871785fd4bac4e6c3c05f130e59","tid":206818,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc136fe30616a27962f171a45b604f3fbedda40","tid":206818,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:35:19.00